---
---
<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-[#0F3E17]">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Left -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="reveal inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.10)] mb-6">
          <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] uppercase text-[#E1F4DF]">Resultado Real</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.5rem] font-light text-white leading-[1.2] mb-5">
          Clínica de Psicologia<br>em São Paulo
        </h2>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 text-[0.9375rem] leading-[1.8] text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.60)] mb-3">
          Antes: 28% de faltas. Confirmações manuais para 35 consultas por semana, consumindo 4h da recepcionista.
        </p>
        <blockquote class="reveal reveal-delay-3 border-l-2 border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.20)] pl-6 mt-8">
          <p class="text-[1rem] italic leading-[1.8] text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.75)] mb-4">
            "Parece óbvio depois que funciona. O difícil foi acreditar que ia ser tão simples de implementar."
          </p>
          <cite class="text-[0.875rem] text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.45)] not-italic">— Dra. Ana Rodrigues, Psicóloga Clínica</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: metrics -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-4">
        {[
          { value: '7%', sub: 'era 28%', label: 'índice de faltas' },
          { value: 'R$ 3.200', sub: null, label: 'receita adicional por mês' },
          { value: '60 dias', sub: null, label: 'para resultado completo' },
        ].map((m, i) => (
          <div
            class="reveal-scale bg-[rgba(255,255,255,0.05)] rounded-[16px] p-8 border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)]"
            style={`transition-delay: ${i * 120}ms`}
          >
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-1">
              <span class="text-[2.75rem] font-light text-white leading-none">{m.value}</span>
              {m.sub && <span class="text-[0.875rem] text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.35)] line-through">{m.sub}</span>}
            </div>
            <p class="text-[0.875rem] text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.50)]">{m.label}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
